I'm looking to pick up a Cycle 460 back card for my T206 back set.  I currently have one but want to send it to a more deserving home.  However I'd rather not create a hole in my collection without knowing what it will take to replace the back type.  If anybody has a Cycle 460 in a PSA 3-5 or SGC 40-60 range for any of the following players, please let me know.  If my lists are correct these all should be available with a Cycle 460 back.  Raw would be fine as well but it should grade out in the desired range.  You'd be making two collectors very happy.
